Improved all 10 agent-atelier plugin skills (candidate, execute, gate, init, monitors, run, status, validate, watchdog, wi) using the creating-skills methodology. Dispatched 10 parallel sub-agents for initial improvements, then ran a 3-CLI peer review (Gemini, Codex, Claude) that identified 7 issues. All 7 issues were resolved: 5 obvious auto-fixes and 2 ambiguous items fixed per recommended best practices. Net result: 449 insertions, 1145 deletions across SKILL.md files plus 8 new reference files.

